00:38:12.700 --> 00:38:20.110
Do you recommend a particular
plugin for e-commerce sites?

00:38:24.700 --> 00:38:28.405
If it's just the code at
compatibility cross-browser

00:38:28.406 --> 00:38:29.640
and cross-os?

00:38:35.135 --> 00:38:36.680
That might be from
