00:38:37.149 --> 00:38:39.100
<v Michelle> I think that one, yes.

00:38:39.100 --> 00:38:40.752
<v Jay> [laughs]

00:38:41.953 --> 00:38:43.350
Oh, here we go.

00:38:43.350 --> 00:38:45.510
We have another question
that just popped up.

00:38:45.510 --> 00:38:49.110
If you had to choose
between video and audio,

00:38:49.110 --> 00:38:53.200
do you think that audio has
a broader appeal than video,

00:38:53.200 --> 00:38:57.670
and would be better to just do the
audio and text, rather than video

00:38:57.670 --> 00:38:58.650
and text?

00:38:58.650 --> 00:39:03.250
<v Michelle> Me personally,
I am an audio and text type person.

00:39:04.940 --> 00:39:09.710
With doing this talk, when it came
to looking at the different things

00:39:09.710 --> 00:39:13.360
with accessibility and
for me on personal,

00:39:13.360 --> 00:39:20.220
I don't know how many times,
I would have an email that's talking

00:39:20.220 --> 00:39:26.440
about a breakthrough for
diabetes care and I'm like, yes,

00:39:26.440 --> 00:39:31.650
let me get to this and it goes
to just a page that is a video,

00:39:31.650 --> 00:39:36.800
that's like 32 minutes long,
no transcript, no closed captioning

00:39:36.800 --> 00:39:39.540
and I'm supposed to watch
this thing for, at least,

00:39:39.540 --> 00:39:44.470
28 minutes before I can
click on a link to take me

00:39:44.470 --> 00:39:47.900
to what they're actually
selling in the information.

00:39:47.900 --> 00:39:51.220
Usually, with those two
minutes in between my ADHD

00:39:51.220 --> 00:39:53.691
and neurodivergent brain, I'm done.

00:39:53.691 --> 00:39:55.510
[laughs]

00:39:56.360 --> 00:40:00.490
But with being a
preschool teacher first,

00:40:00.490 --> 00:40:06.270
and then I've taught beginner's
WordPress and then in a trainer

00:40:06.270 --> 00:40:12.140
at work for our team, there's so
much more beneficial to the mixture

00:40:13.610 --> 00:40:14.730
of things.

00:40:14.730 --> 00:40:19.830
I like it so much more where you
can just listen to the audio,

00:40:19.830 --> 00:40:23.270
you can just read or you can do
the video or you can do the mix

00:40:23.270 --> 00:40:24.410
of all three.

00:40:24.410 --> 00:40:28.080
If I had to choose, especially
the, I'm just going to stand here

00:40:28.080 --> 00:40:31.970
and talk to my video or
the not have an option,

00:40:31.970 --> 00:40:33.090
give me just the audio.

00:40:33.090 --> 00:40:34.090
[laughs]

00:40:34.500 --> 00:40:36.710
<v Jay> I'm exactly the same way.

00:40:36.710 --> 00:40:38.923
If it's just going
to be talking at me,

00:40:38.924 --> 00:40:40.860
I'd much rather have a transcript.

00:40:40.860 --> 00:40:42.674
I agree with that one.

